  <brief_title>Acupuncture for Post-stroke Shoulder-hand Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Acupuncture and Traditional Chinese Medicine Combined With Rehabilitation Therapy for Post-stroke Shoulder-hand Syndrome in Community Hospital: a Multicenter，Randomized，Controlled Trial</official_title>
